HEADWORD: Brecciated
<hw>Brec"ci*a`ted</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Consisting of
angular fragments cemented together; resembling breccia in
appearance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>brecciated</qex> appearance of many specimens [of
meteorites].</q> <rj><qau>H. A. Newton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

